Dialogue: 100,0:03:03.06,0:03:05.73,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}感觉就像昨天她还想搞死我们\N{\fnArial\fs48}It feels like yesterday she was trying to kill us.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:05.97,0:03:08.00,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不，不，那是好几周之前\N{\fnArial\fs48}No, no, that was several weeks ago.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:08.00,0:03:08.64,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}坐标！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Coordinates!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:08.97,0:03:11.17,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们还需要融合簇的具体坐标\N{\fnArial\fs48}We still need the cluster's exact coordinates
Dialogue: 100,0:03:11.17,0:03:12.09,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}才能开钻！\N{\fnArial\fs48}in order to drill!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:12.57,0:03:15.46,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}有个钻石基地可能包含这个信息，\N{\fnArial\fs48}There's a diamond base that may hold that information,
Dialogue: 100,0:03:15.66,0:03:17.42,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但前往那里将会非常困难\N{\fnArial\fs48}but getting there is going to be difficult.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:17.64,0:03:18.20,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}怎么会？\N{\fnArial\fs48}How come?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:18.57,0:03:20.68,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}因为那里无法通过传送台到达，而且它在...\N{\fnArial\fs48}Because it's not accessible by warp pad, and it's on...
Dialogue: 100,0:03:23.82,0:03:26.06,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}月球？！\N{\fnArial\fs48}The moon?!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:26.57,0:03:27.84,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}没错，史蒂文，月球\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yeah, Steven, the moon.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:28.51,0:03:31.33,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}狮子，你给我们制造一个通向月球的超级传送吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Lion, can you make us a special super warp to the moon?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:34.12,0:03:35.26,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}来吧，狮子！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Come on, Lion!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:35.26,0:03:37.15,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们必须做这个才能阻止融合簇！\N{\fnArial\fs48}We got to do this to stop the cluster!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:37.33,0:03:39.31,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}如果我们做不到，那就不不会有什么地球了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}If we don't, there's gonna be no more earth!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:39.57,0:03:41.80,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不会有朋友间的快乐时光！\N{\fnArial\fs48}No more fun times with your pals!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:41.82,0:03:43.55,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不会有狮子棒棒糖？\N{\fnArial\fs48}No more Lion Lickers?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:43.75,0:03:44.82,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不会有懒觉了？\N{\fnArial\fs48}No more naps?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:49.97,0:03:50.91,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}看来是“懒觉”\N{\fnArial\fs48}Guess it was "naps."
Dialogue: 100,0:03:58.47,0:04:00.48,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}挺酷的，对吧？！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Pretty cool, right?!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:07.02,0:04:10.29,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}上，狮子，上！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Go, Lion, go!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:20.08,0:04:22.53,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}狮子！你还好吗，伙计？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Lion! Are you okay, bud?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:24.06,0:04:26.60,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}让我从这个毛茸茸的怪胎里出来-呃！嗷！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Get me out of this furry freak -- ugh! Ow!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:27.62,0:04:30.53,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦，狮子，你为自己赢得了一周的懒觉！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Aw, Lion, you've earned your naps for the week!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:32.71,0:04:33.40,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们做到了\N{\fnArial\fs48}We made it.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:33.82,0:04:35.51,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这看起来不像是月球啊\N{\fnArial\fs48}It doesn't look like the moon.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:36.24,0:04:38.13,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嘿，看这里，我觉得这是个门！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hey, look over here. I think it's a door!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:40.68,0:04:41.95,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃...对！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Uh...Yep!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:42.40,0:04:43.80,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们在月球上！\N{\fnArial\fs48}We on the moon!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:44.08,0:04:46.88,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}紫晶，求求你别把我们吸到太空中了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Amethyst, please don't blow us into space!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:48.03,0:04:48.86,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}喔！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Whoa!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:53.43,0:04:54.24,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}看看我！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Look at me!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:54.64,0:04:56.86,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我是月球小子！\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm a moon boy!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:57.73,0:04:59.62,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哈哈！好的，月球小子！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ha ha! All right, moon boy!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:02.06,0:05:03.88,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}月球小子，四重后空翻！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Moon boy, quadruple backflip!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:04.44,0:05:05.40,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嘿！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hey!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:05.62,0:05:07.11,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我没什么就不能是月球小子？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Why can't I be a moon boy?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:07.33,0:05:08.44,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们是宝石人\N{\fnArial\fs48}We're gems.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:08.73,0:05:09.93,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们是太空种族\N{\fnArial\fs48}We're a space-faring race
Dialogue: 100,0:05:09.93,0:05:11.62,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们被设计为便于征服其他世界的！\N{\fnArial\fs48}designed to conquer other worlds!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:11.84,0:05:13.68,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们的身体形态会自动根据\N{\fnArial\fs48}Our physical forms adjust automatically
Dialogue: 100,0:05:13.68,0:05:15.75,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}任何星球的重力进行调整！\N{\fnArial\fs48}to the gravity of any planetoid!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:15.91,0:05:17.57,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}噢，真矬！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Aw, lame!
Dialogue: 200,0:05:18.00,0:05:20.26,Song Lyrics Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn华文楷体\fs64}我有天在月球瞎蹦\N{\fnArial\fs48}♪ I was bouncing on the moon one day ♪
Dialogue: 600,0:05:18.00,0:05:20.26,Hint,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,100)}此处曲调源自“Fountain in the Park”\N与尤金·塞尔南和哈里森·施密特1972年阿波罗17号舱外活动中所唱的类似
Dialogue: 100,0:05:22.40,0:05:22.77,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:23.22,0:05:25.86,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嘿，橄榄石，那应该是谁？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hey, Peridot, who is this supposed to be?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:27.57,0:05:29.48,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那是蓝钻石！\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's blue diamond!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:29.68,0:05:31.66,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}等等，她们都在这里？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Wait. Are they all here?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:31.82,0:05:32.84,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}啊，对！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ah, yes!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:32.84,0:05:33.86,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她在那！\N{\fnArial\fs48}There she is!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:34.04,0:05:34.46,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}谁？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Who?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:36.37,0:05:40.08,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}请看，黄钻石！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Behold, yellow diamond!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:40.33,0:05:41.60,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她很雄伟吧？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Isn't she magnificent?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:41.98,0:05:43.28,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}喔！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Wow!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:43.60,0:05:46.17,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那么，钻石是什么？\N{\fnArial\fs48}So, who are the diamonds anyway?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:46.48,0:05:47.64,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她们看起来很重要！\N{\fnArial\fs48}They seem like a big deal!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:48.02,0:05:49.13,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你在开玩笑吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Are you joking me?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:49.39,0:05:51.33,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}钻石是宝石人们的母亲！\N{\fnArial\fs48}The diamonds are the gem matriarchs!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:51.53,0:05:53.73,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她们一起组成了伟大的钻石政权\N{\fnArial\fs48}Together they make up the great diamond authority
Dialogue: 100,0:05:53.73,0:05:56.42,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}掌管着母世界与所有偏远的殖民地！\N{\fnArial\fs48}that governs homeworld and all the outlying colonies!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:56.76,0:05:58.31,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们只为服务她们！\N{\fnArial\fs48}We live to serve them!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:01.82,0:06:04.33,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我-我指，我们最初的目的是服务她们\N{\fnArial\fs48}I -- I mean, we were all made to serve them
Dialogue: 100,0:06:04.33,0:06:07.17,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}只是一部分人不再如此\N{\fnArial\fs48}even though some of us don't anymore.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:08.24,0:06:10.35,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嘿，我觉得那是控制界面！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hey, I think that's a control surface over there!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:10.53,0:06:11.39,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们看看吧！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Let's take a look!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:11.39,0:06:12.04,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}好啊！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yeah!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:13.64,0:06:14.84,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我感觉这样才对\N{\fnArial\fs48}I think this is right.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:15.20,0:06:17.62,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这里的材料与周围的石头不同\N{\fnArial\fs48}The material is different from the surrounding stone.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:17.91,0:06:20.66,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我感觉如果我...这么做！\N{\fnArial\fs48}I think if I just do...This!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:31.86,0:06:33.17,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这真是太神奇了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}This is so incredible!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:33.66,0:06:36.37,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}只有精英中的精英才能深入这里\N{\fnArial\fs48}Only the most elite of the elite can enter these sanctums.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:36.60,0:06:39.51,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们真的是在沿着钻石们的足迹！\N{\fnArial\fs48}We are literally walking in the footsteps of the diamonds.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:39.93,0:06:41.86,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她们肯定非常喜欢台阶\N{\fnArial\fs48}They must really like stairs.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:44.91,0:06:46.51,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嘿，这是什么房间？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hey, what's this room?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:47.38,0:06:48.86,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这不是我们此行的目的\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's not what we came for.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:49.24,0:06:52.11,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们能快点吗？这地方让我不爽\N{\fnArial\fs48}Can we hurry it up? This place gives me the creeps.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:59.08,0:07:01.02,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们真的在月球上了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}We really are on the moon!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:01.64,0:07:02.53,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦，我的天哪！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, my goodness!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:02.73,0:07:04.37,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这看起来还是全新的！\N{\fnArial\fs48}This looks like it could be brand-new!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:04.63,0:07:06.71,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我是指，按现在的标准这是古董，\N{\fnArial\fs48}I mean, it's a relic by today's standards,
Dialogue: 100,0:07:06.71,0:07:08.68,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但，妈呀，这真是如此优雅，\N{\fnArial\fs48}but, golly, it's so elegant,
Dialogue: 100,0:07:08.68,0:07:10.60,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}如此简洁，如此完美！\N{\fnArial\fs48}so simple, so perfect!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:10.83,0:07:11.97,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那么，你能打开它吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}So, how do you turn it on?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:12.93,0:07:14.02,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我不会\N{\fnArial\fs48}I have no idea.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:15.02,0:07:17.33,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嘿，这有个发光的手形界面哎！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hey, it's got one of those glowy hand dealies!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:17.66,0:07:18.57,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你不能坐在那里！\N{\fnArial\fs48}You can't sit there!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:18.88,0:07:20.60,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}为什么不？这真的很酷！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Why not? It's really cool!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:20.91,0:07:23.37,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那个椅子只为了给最尊贵的宝石人！\N{\fnArial\fs48}That chair is only for the most elite gems!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:23.53,0:07:25.66,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你不能随便坐到精英该坐的地方！\N{\fnArial\fs48}You can't go around sitting where an elite would sit!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:25.95,0:07:28.57,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不过，她们现在不在，对吧？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Well, they aren't here now, right?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:35.24,0:07:37.22,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嘿，这个玩意是做什么的？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hey, what's this doodad for?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:37.37,0:07:38.15,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}把它放回去！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Put that back!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:38.80,0:07:40.80,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嗯，好吧，我们看看\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hmm, okay, let's see here.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:41.22,0:07:42.03,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}开始吧\N{\fnArial\fs48}There we go.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:42.44,0:07:44.15,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这是个非常古老的系统\N{\fnArial\fs48}This is a really old system.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:44.37,0:07:48.75,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}得找到正确的文件...\N{\fnArial\fs48}Gotta find the right file...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:48.75,0:07:49.31,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}啊哈！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Aha!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:49.84,0:07:52.46,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}融合簇，融合簇，你在哪里，融合簇？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Cluster, cluster, where are you, cluster?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:52.97,0:07:53.57,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}啊哈！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Aha!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:53.57,0:07:55.00,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这里是注入点！\N{\fnArial\fs48}There's the insertion point!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:55.02,0:07:57.55,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}看来是在切面九的第二幼儿园\N{\fnArial\fs48}Looks like the beta kindergarten in facet nine.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:57.91,0:07:59.13,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那是两个中较小的那个，\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's the smaller of the two,
Dialogue: 100,0:07:59.13,0:08:01.73,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}一点不如你出生的那个出色，紫晶！\N{\fnArial\fs48}not nearly as impressive as yours, Amethyst!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:01.93,0:08:03.62,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃，谢谢？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Uh, thanks?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:03.88,0:08:05.71,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但融合簇现在在哪呢？\N{\fnArial\fs48}But where is the cluster now?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:06.04,0:08:06.60,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}等下\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hang on.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:07.95,0:08:08.66,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}它在那！\N{\fnArial\fs48}There it is!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:08.88,0:08:10.11,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}它深深的嵌入了地幔之中\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's embedded deep in the mantle.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:10.60,0:08:13.80,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}相对于谷仓，它大概2500单位深\N{\fnArial\fs48}Relative to the barn, it's roughly 2,500 units down.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:14.06,0:08:16.17,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们需要做的就是将数据输入钻头，\N{\fnArial\fs48}All we need to do is feed this data to the drill,
Dialogue: 100,0:08:16.17,0:08:17.40,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}然后就可以出发了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}and we should be all set!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:17.80,0:08:18.62,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那么就这样吧！\N{\fnArial\fs48}That's it, then!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:18.87,0:08:20.13,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}任务完成！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Mission accomplished!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:20.13,0:08:21.47,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}好的，团队！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yeah, team!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:21.47,0:08:22.54,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}太好了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Great.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:22.54,0:08:24.04,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}让我们赶快离开这里吧！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Let's get the heck out of here!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:24.40,0:08:25.24,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}等等，别走！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Wait. Hold on!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:25.66,0:08:27.31,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这东西上有游戏吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Does this thing have any games on it?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:27.57,0:08:28.26,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不，不，不，不\N{\fnArial\fs48}No, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:28.46,0:08:30.44,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这不是用来玩的\N{\fnArial\fs48}This wasn't used for games.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:30.44,0:08:30.93,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}唉\N{\fnArial\fs48}Aw.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:31.15,0:08:32.75,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}它之前被用于规划殖民地\N{\fnArial\fs48}It was used for planning the colony.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:33.00,0:08:34.02,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这里，看！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Here, look!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:35.86,0:08:37.35,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这是所有建造在\N{\fnArial\fs48}So here's a map of all structures
Dialogue: 100,0:08:37.35,0:08:38.68,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}地球上的建筑的分布图\N{\fnArial\fs48}that were originally built on earth.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:39.37,0:08:41.46,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}说实话，这可能只占\N{\fnArial\fs48}All told, this probably only accounts
Dialogue: 100,0:08:41.46,0:08:43.77,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}原本规划的数量的5%\N{\fnArial\fs48}for maybe 5% of what was originally planned!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:44.31,0:08:45.31,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}原来的计划是什么？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What was the plan?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:45.73,0:08:47.06,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那么，让我们看一看\N{\fnArial\fs48}Well, let's take a look.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:55.17,0:08:56.71,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}一个建成的地球殖民地！\N{\fnArial\fs48}A finished earth colony!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:57.64,0:08:59.13,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}喔！看这个！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Wow! Look at this!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:59.35,0:09:02.97,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}89个幼儿园，67座尖塔，每个切面一座星际传送台\N{\fnArial\fs48}89 kindergartens, 67 spires, a galaxy warp in each facet,
Dialogue: 100,0:09:03.13,0:09:05.28,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}有效利用一切可用资源\N{\fnArial\fs48}efficient use of all available materials.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:05.44,0:09:07.95,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你们怎么想的，要停止这个计划？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What were you thinking shutting this operation down!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:07.95,0:09:09.40,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这本可以很伟大的！\N{\fnArial\fs48}It could have been great!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:09.42,0:09:11.11,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不，你错了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}No, you're wrong!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:11.35,0:09:12.26,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你什么意思？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:12.48,0:09:14.13,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这多完美，看！\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's perfect. Look at it!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:14.37,0:09:16.55,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们就在看啊\N{\fnArial\fs48}We are looking at it.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:16.77,0:09:18.37,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}对，这个计划太臭了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yeah, this plan stinks!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:18.62,0:09:20.15,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}完成这个殖民地意味着\N{\fnArial\fs48}Completing this colony would have meant
Dialogue: 100,0:09:20.15,0:09:22.33,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}地球生命的灭绝\N{\fnArial\fs48}the extinction of all life on earth.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:22.77,0:09:24.62,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但想想它带来的好处-\N{\fnArial\fs48}But think of the good it would have done --
Dialogue: 100,0:09:24.97,0:09:26.42,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}本可制造出的宝石人，\N{\fnArial\fs48}the gems would that would have been made,
Dialogue: 100,0:09:26.73,0:09:28.37,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们帝国的扩张！\N{\fnArial\fs48}our empire expanded!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:28.61,0:09:31.48,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}玫瑰石英相信所有的生命都非常宝贵\N{\fnArial\fs48}Rose Quartz believed all life was precious
Dialogue: 100,0:09:31.48,0:09:33.28,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}且值得保护！\N{\fnArial\fs48}and worth protecting!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:33.68,0:09:35.02,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那么，如果她想保护，\N{\fnArial\fs48}Well, if she wanted to protect it,
Dialogue: 100,0:09:35.02,0:09:36.82,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那可算是个糟糕的结局啊！\N{\fnArial\fs48}she did a lousy job!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:36.95,0:09:39.57,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}如果地球还是个殖民地就不会有融合簇了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}There'd be no cluster if the earth had stayed a colony!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:39.86,0:09:42.86,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}现在殖民地消失了，地球也不会存来了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Now there's no colony, and there's gonna be no earth!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:42.97,0:09:46.11,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}真感谢你，玫瑰石英-你毁了这个星球！\N{\fnArial\fs48}So thank you, Rose Quartz -- you doomed the planet!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:49.62,0:09:50.53,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh!
Dialogue: 200,0:09:51.24,0:09:53.15,Song Lyrics Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn华文楷体\fs64}有什么能够比得上-\N{\fnArial\fs48}♪ Is there anything that's worth more than -- ♪
Dialogue: 100,0:09:53.55,0:09:55.86,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你给我听着\N{\fnArial\fs48}You listen to me now.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:57.31,0:10:00.55,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你在谈论一些你丝毫不理解的事情\N{\fnArial\fs48}You are talking about things that you do not understand.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:00.80,0:10:02.84,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}石榴，住手，求你了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Garnet, stop, please!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:03.55,0:10:04.57,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这不值得\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's not worth it.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:04.97,0:10:05.75,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}任务完成了\N{\fnArial\fs48}We're done here.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:05.75,0:10:07.11,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}让我们回家吧\N{\fnArial\fs48}Let's just go home.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:15.17,0:10:16.06,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我说什么了？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What'd I say?!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:16.51,0:10:18.02,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我只不过在陈述事实而已！\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm just stating a fact!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:18.20,0:10:21.02,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}叛乱并没有真正拯救地球\N{\fnArial\fs48}The rebellion didn't really save earth.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:21.17,0:10:22.95,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那只是推迟了不可避免的结局而已\N{\fnArial\fs48}It just delayed the inevitable.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:23.31,0:10:24.77,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她们不是这么看的\N{\fnArial\fs48}That's not the way they see it.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:25.37,0:10:27.00,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她们花了几千年时间\N{\fnArial\fs48}They've spent thousands of years
Dialogue: 100,0:10:27.02,0:10:28.11,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}试着保护地球\N{\fnArial\fs48}trying to protect the earth.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:28.82,0:10:31.42,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我以为也许你最终能理解原因的\N{\fnArial\fs48}I thought maybe you finally understood why.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:38.51,0:10:39.20,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}橄榄石！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Peridot!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:39.77,0:10:41.00,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}干嘛？我来了\N{\fnArial\fs48}What? I'm coming.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:45.80,0:10:46.73,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}赶紧的，你们两个\N{\fnArial\fs48}Let's go, you two.
